name: //Grunge Dreams// Sunday Morning
description: After left nothing behind, no one alive and the ghost of the last war she started to experience different kind of emotional rutines: The melancholia, the gloom, the dream, and quite often the desire to find someone. The experience she wanted to feel was the essence of the morning, the only morning that the human been wanted for once feel free and not imprisoned in their own emotional tragedy.  //Unknown IA mother, possibly self-destructed//
